0.060   2018-12-05 (PERLANCAR)

	- [refactor] Extract list of options to module so it's usable by
	  other code.


0.05    2016-10-21 (PERLANCAR)

	- Allow script to be detected by Getopt::Long::util as Getopt::Long
	  script.


0.04    2015-09-17 (PERLANCAR)

	- Adjust to Complete::Util 0.36 (complete_file() split to
	  Complete-File).


0.03    2015-08-11 (PERLANCAR)

	- Use ShellCompleter::Util to be more DRY, complete the rest of the
	  options' values.

	- [pod] Don't linkify non-perl program mpv because they generally
	  won't work in MetaCPAN etc.


0.02    2015-08-06 (PERLANCAR)

        - Remove the use of Log::Any to reduce startup overhead.

        - [doc] Mention the version of mpv supported.


0.01    2015-08-06 (PERLANCAR)

	- First release (not all option values are completed yet, boy mpv has a
          LOT of options).
